hei - hi
welkommen - welcome
takk - please and thank you
-------------------------------------
vann - water
eller - or
og - and
kaffe - coffe
Te - tea
vin - wine
øl - beer
melk - milk
brød - bread, load of bread
--------------------------------------
*det - that, it, those, the, they, there, what, so

ha det - bye, goodbye, so long
--------------------------------------
*eller - or

ja - yes
nei - no
ja eller nei - yes or no
--------------------------------------
mor - mother 
far - father
bror - brother
søster - sister
--------------------------------------
en - a 
en mor - a mother
en far - a father
bror - a brother
søster - a sister
--------------------------------------
faren - the father 
moren - the mother 
broren - the brother
sønnen - the son 
datteren - the daughter 
søsteren - the sister
--------------------------------------
min - my, mine 

datteren min - my daugther 
søsteren min - my sister
broren min - my brother
faren min - my father
--------------------------------------
er du Maria? - are you Maria?

er - are
du - you
--------------------------------------
veldig - very
snill - nice
Du er snill - You're nice
høy - tall
--------------------------------------
Moren min er vedy snill - My mother is very nice
smart - smart

--------------------------------------
